ZH: 农民用牛粪来施肥。
EN: Farmers use cow dung as fertilizer.

ZH: 这块地被牛粪覆盖了。
EN: This patch of land is covered with cow dung.

ZH: 家里的花草都在牛粪的滋养下长得很好。
EN: The flowers and plants at home are thriving under the nourishment of cow dung.

ZH: 牛粪有时会被作为燃料使用。
EN: Cow dung is sometimes used as fuel.

ZH: 清洁工人正在清理街道上的牛粪。
EN: The janitor is cleaning up the cow dung on the street.

ZH: 这里真的有很多牛粪味。
EN: There is really a strong odor of cow dung here.

ZH: 农田中撒满了牛粪，农作物长势喜人。
EN: The farmland is covered with cow dung, and the crops are growing vigorously.

ZH: 这里喂养了很多奶牛，所以到处都是牛粪。
EN: There are a lot of cow dung everywhere because many cows are raised here.

ZH: 农民将牛粪收集起来用于生物能源的生产。
EN: Farmers collect cow dung for the production of bioenergy.

ZH: 这种肥料里混合了牛粪和其他有机物质。
EN: This fertilizer is a mixture of cow dung and other organic materials.

ZH: 在农村，牛粪被用来做土地改良剂。
EN: In rural areas, cow dung is used as a soil improver.

ZH: 这种肥料富含牛粪的营养成分。
EN: This fertilizer is rich in nutrients derived from cow dung.

ZH: 请小心，地上有牛粪。
EN: Please be careful, there is cow dung on the ground.

ZH: 这块土地怎么这么多牛粪？
EN: Why is there so much cow dung on this piece of land?

ZH: 这个农场每天产生大量的牛粪。
EN: This farm produces a large amount of cow dung every day.

ZH: 牛粪被广泛地用于有机农业。
EN: Cow dung is widely used in organic farming.

ZH: 春天是撒牛粪的好时机。
EN: Spring is a good time to spread cow dung.

ZH: 牛粪可以制成高品质的有机肥料。
EN: Cow dung can be processed into high-quality organic fertilizers.

ZH: 这些农作物都依靠牛粪来生长。
EN: These crops rely on cow dung for their growth.

ZH: 农民使用牛粪来改善土地质量。
EN: Farmers use cow dung to improve the quality of the land.
